high_descs: Move to the right sink on the right, to the right cabinet under the sink.
Pick up the soap in the right cabinet under the sink.
Bring the soap to the middle of the sink.
Put the soap in the middle of the sink, turn on the water.
Bring the soap to the tub on the left.
Put the soap in the tub.
anns.task_desc: Put a soap in the tub.

high_descs: Turn right head to the sink cabinet
Open the cabinet below the sink on the right, pick up a soap then close it
Move to the front then turn left move a little then turn right to the sink
Put the soap in the left side of the sink and rinse it
Turn right then head to the tub
Put the soap in the tub
anns.task_desc: Put the clean soap in the tub

high_descs: Turn to your right and walk towards the bathtub, then turn right at the second bathroom sink on your left.
Open the cabinet under the right sink and remove the bar of soap inside.
Move over to the sink on your left.
Place the bar of soap in the sink, turn the water on, rinse the bar of soap off, turn the water off, and remove the bar of soap from the sink.
Turn to your right and go to the bath tub across from you.
Place the bar of soap into the bath tub.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean bar of soap in the bath tub.
